{"tid":1162904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑名單禁令！華為連電腦都無得出？","createTime":"2019-05-20T06:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T06:41:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"03cf0bdb88307713aec91d4378f50a2e55883c04","tid":1162904,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"美國政府上周五簽署針對華為的黑名單，今日第一個工作日，除了 Google 表示要停止與華為合作外， 多家有向華為提供晶片的美資公司，包括 Intel 、 Qualcomm 、 Xilinx 及 Broadcom 等公司，都有向僱員發出指引，指明未得到新的指示之前，都不得向華為提供硬件或軟件服務。<br />\n<br />\n以供應鏈看，目前在華為的業務上， Intel 是主要的伺服器處理器供應商， Qualcomm 則提供手機處理器及數據機晶片， Xilinx 主要提供編程晶片以用於網絡產品上，而 Broadcom 則是主要的路由晶片供應商。<br />\n<br />\n因此，今次禁令不單影響華為手機業務，連網絡及電腦產品也會受到嚴重影響，特別是未來一段時間全球通訊商都要為 5G 網絡鋪路，此舉不單會令華為不能在美國爭到 5G 市場，也影響著華為 5G 網絡在歐洲的競爭能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/05/20/%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%EF%BC%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%80%A3%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%97%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2019%2F05%2F20%2F%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4%25EF%25BC%2581%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E9%2583%25BD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2587%25BA%25EF%25BC%259F%2F&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ11KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=775cc4f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/05/20/%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4%EF%BC%81%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%80%A3%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E5%BE%97%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%9F/</a>"},{"pid":"df32edf41ae3ebaee845e74f6738fb57603725b4","tid":1162904,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"唔係講到自己技術好高咩 點解要倚賴人地"},{"pid":"542cb72a0cf3f31e9cb65b4729b48467c53a3fdd","tid":1162904,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"有麒麟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\"